{"text_id":125710,"tokens":["In"," this"," paper",","," we"," propose"," a"," novel"," deep"," convolutional"," neural"," network"," (","CNN",")"," -","based"," algorithm"," for"," solving"," ill","-","posed"," inverse"," problems","."," Regular","ized"," iterative"," algorithms"," have"," emerged"," as"," the"," standard"," approach"," to"," ill","-","posed"," inverse"," problems","."," However",","," these"," algorithms"," have"," their"," limitations",","," including"," slow"," convergence"," rates"," and"," sensitivity"," to"," initialization","."," Deep"," learning","-","based"," methods"," have"," shown"," promise"," in"," solving"," these"," issues",","," but"," most"," existing"," methods"," rely"," on"," fully"," connected"," layers"," or"," shallow"," networks","."," Our"," proposed"," algorithm"," utilizes"," a"," fully"," convolutional"," architecture",","," which"," can"," efficiently"," learn"," high","-","level"," information"," from"," low","-","level"," features","."," It"," also"," employs"," a"," residual"," learning"," framework",","," which"," speeds"," up"," convergence"," and"," enhances"," the"," stability"," of"," the"," algorithm","."," Additionally",","," by"," incorporating"," a"," skip"," connection"," into"," the"," network",","," our"," algorithm"," can"," leverage"," prior"," knowledge"," and"," improve"," accuracy"," in"," the"," reconstruction"," process","."," We"," tested"," our"," algorithm"," on"," several"," different"," inverse"," problems",","," including"," image"," de","blur","ring"," and"," super","-","resolution",","," and"," achieved"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," performance"," compared"," to"," other"," deep"," learning"," methods"," and"," traditional"," iterative"," algorithms","."," Our"," proposed"," algorithm"," has"," potential"," applications"," in"," medical"," imaging",","," remote"," sensing",","," and"," computer"," vision","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}